Class StorageLevelSerializer

    org.nd4j.shade.jackson.databind.jsonFormatVisitors.JsonFormatVisitable

    public class StorageLevelSerializer
extends org.nd4j.shade.jackson.databind.JsonSerializer<org.apache.spark.storage.StorageLevel>
    By default: Spark storage levels don't serialize/deserialize cleanly with Jackson (i.e., we can get different results out). So we'll manually control the serialization/deserialization for StorageLevel objects
    Author:
    Alex Black
